thread.title_full: Peaches Boutique reviewed by Journye Goeman

author: Journye Goeman
title: Journye Goeman
text: I absolutely love my dress. I was worried about ordering online especially on something so expensive. However after measuring myself at home and using the sizing chart it fits perfectly. The dress also arrived after 4 days even with a storm in my area. The dress was of great quality.
